{"tid":4291,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"阿聯猶轉機方唔方便？","createTime":"2016-11-26T12:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T12:58:11.000Z","uid":16531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40f16d170c37f5c89e0e716b93b69f110b693d53","tid":4291,"uid":16531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"我fd諗住搭阿聯猶去英國<br />\n但買左之後開始擔心唔識轉機 （佢未搭過飛機)<br />\n我自己搭過一次 但全程跟足指示牌無咩難度<br />\n所以我都唔知有咩注意地方講佢知<br />\n聽人講有時去第二個gate要搭地鐵<br />\n想問下各位覺得有啲咩要注意"},{"pid":"25119363a5c5001a906dc2e55c88b386176e5b0b","tid":4291,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我fd諗住搭阿聯猶去英國<br />\n但買左之後開始擔心唔識轉機 （佢未搭過飛機)<br />\n我自己搭過一次 但全程跟足指示牌無咩難度<br />\n所以我都唔知有咩注意地方講佢知<br />\n聽人講有時去第二個gate要搭地鐵<br />\n想問下各位覺得有啲咩要注意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有服務可以叫航空公司全程搵個空姐帶佢上機轉機<br />\n不過通常係唔識英文既阿婆先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858d44794ffeb2f0eb34b448beb4a72aa26adbdd","tid":4291,"uid":5039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"睇你係邊轉 <br />\n上次得一個鐘係杜拜轉機<br />\n要轉terminal差啲趕唔切"},{"pid":"3abd90b1b6c7e93d20fb8a245cc4cbfd99b0a0c0","tid":4291,"uid":16531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"係咪落機求奇搵個空姐就得<br />\n佢話訂飛陣無"},{"pid":"29241f9c948b88d8b6d3cb365e9de974d89fa260","tid":4291,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"通常落機都要check一check手提行李<br />\n跟住搭無人駕駛列車去返轉機個閘口<br />\n個閘口喺A/B區嘅話 就好易搵<br />\nC區就要行好撚遠<br />\n搵閘口就自己睇牌對航班編號<br />\n轉機有兩三個鐘就可以慢慢黎<br />\n一個鐘就要行快兩步<br />\n香港delay咗唔使驚<br />\n去到佢會有指示<br />\n叫你去counter攞張新機票上最快出發嗰班機 (冇記錯會係check行李前就攞咗)"},{"pid":"f08dd5ac6913617b509a0a4b7f0a63ae6f0bc6ab","tid":4291,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揀啲有4個鐘轉既咪好啲<br />\n又可以行下買下野"},{"pid":"88c3bf1e621dba876c569d9428e4deefc77a0fd7","tid":4291,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:10:12.000Z","msg":"杜拜好撚方便喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897d9f87311633e1ec39b787e286a5f102e84e98","tid":4291,"uid":16531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜拜好撚方便喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢女仔第一次遠行同轉機 我諗佢有啲擔心姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a75d6be7510c1711ef3680591c8c025d634b78","tid":4291,"uid":16531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T20:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常落機都要check一check手提行李<br />\n跟住搭無人駕駛列車去返轉機個閘口<br />\n個閘口喺A/B區嘅話 就好易搵<br />\nC區就要行好撚遠<br />\n搵閘口就自己睇牌對航班編號<br />\n轉機有兩三個鐘就可以慢慢黎<br />\n一個鐘就要行快兩步<br />\n香港delay咗唔使驚<br />\n去到佢會有指示<br />\n叫你去counter攞張新機票上最快出發嗰班機 (冇記錯會係check行李前就攞咗)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThank you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好詳細"},{"pid":"bfe47cb507176ba4de48d4496617574dc676b855","tid":4291,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7bd47b9d01fec5157d55516cce40a854dbde86","tid":4291,"uid":29226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過幾日我都要係阿聯猶轉機"},{"pid":"4c348dc1a98ab7e8f7e00004903658c3b4f7666f","tid":4291,"uid":16531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T22:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi 終於轉會啦？ <br />\n其實哥個我女友黎 1月8日黎英國搵我 <br />\n但我9號考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBetween 我寫緊篇essay仲有700字寫完 遲少少覆pm sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825b5bb697eb631f75a1dba1e03aef2f4693deb2","tid":4291,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"講多少少先 如果兩程都係emirates就easy la<br />\n我之前emirates轉fly dubai就要坐shuttles去另一個terminal <br />\n上車位有d亂 因為同落機搭shuttles落車係同一個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係架架都得 要等佢指示 人又多 困死係果個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8650897fde32a606ddde09e4f466196fb73fd5e","tid":4291,"uid":25116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:13:42.000Z","msg":"之前阿聯猶杜拜轉機，等候over 4 hrs 係可以攞餐卷食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29add5113ac450ca40117fa7836ffcf36e380029","tid":4291,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi 終於轉會啦？ <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實哥個我女友黎</span> 1月8日黎英國搵我 <br />\n但我9號考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBetween 我寫緊篇essay仲有700字寫完 遲少少覆pm sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}